{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5Y2O5YGl_NjEwNg_0008","text":"即使世界再大 即使去到那兒 這些細節大志 沒誰知 沒誰知","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":24},"semantics":{"themes":["友誼","價值觀","獨特性"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["世界","細節","大志","沒誰知"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,9,4,4,4,2,3,9,4,4,5,0,5,3,4,4,2,4,2,0,3,2,0,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zik1","si2","sai3","gaai3","zoi3","daai6","zik1","si2","heoi3","dou3","naa5","ji4","ze5","se1","sai3","zit3","daai6","zi3","mut6","seoi4","zi1","mut6","seoi4","zi1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"即使","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"世界","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"再大","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"即使","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"去","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"那兒","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"這些","pos":"DET"},{"text":"細節","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"大志","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"沒","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"誰知","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"沒","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"誰知","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"這句使用排比句式「即使...即使...」，強調無論世界多大、去到哪裡，這些只有自己和朋友才懂的「細節」和「大志」是別人無法理解的，突顯友誼的獨特性。"},"source":{"title":"小圈子","artists":["周華健"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6106","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5Y2O5YGl_NjEwNg_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5Y2O5YGl_NjEwNg_0009","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_5ZGo5Y2O5YGl_NjEwNg_0009","text":"寂寞時候別太快便酒醉 否則苦水不知吐向誰","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":19},"semantics":{"themes":["孤獨","尋求慰藉","友誼"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["寂寞","酒醉","苦水","吐向誰"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,0,2,2,4,4,2,9,4,9,3,9,9,3,3,4,4,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zik6","mok6","si4","hau6","bit6","taai3","faai3","bin6","zau2","zeoi3","fau2","zak1","fu2","seoi2","bat1","zi1","tou3","hoeng3","seoi4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"寂寞","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"時候","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"別太快","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"便","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"酒醉","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"否則","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"苦水","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不知","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"吐","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"向","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"誰","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"這句描述了在寂寞時尋求麻醉（酒醉），但卻不知道苦水該向誰傾訴，暗示了孤獨的無助感。"},"source":{"title":"小圈子","artists":["周華健"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6106","prev_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5Y2O5YGl_NjEwNg_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_5ZGo5Y2O5YGl_NjEwNg_0010","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
